hawk-future-21%26ascsubtag%3Dhawk-custom-tracking-21\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"Amazon UK\" data-merchant-id=\"1027\" data-merchant-network=\"Amazon\" data-merchant-url=\"amazon.co.uk\"\u003e\u003cu\u003eperennial ryegrass (£9.99 at Amazon)\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e. Ideally, it should not look like a rewilded lawn or meadow, instead just like a regular lawn that has always existed,’ explains Graham Smith MCIHort, a gardening expert from \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://mailtrack.io/l/58e1c42d033dea3b9168aa56205567916126c7b2?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lbsbuyersguide.co.uk%2F\u0026amp;u=10263400\u0026amp;signature=b22ea0c075184700\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-url=\"https://mailtrack.io/l/58e1c42d033dea3b9168aa56205567916126c7b2?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lbsbuyersguide.co.uk%2F\u0026amp;u=10263400\u0026amp;signature=b22ea0c075184700\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"none\"\u003e\u003cu\u003eLBS Horticulture\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘There is potential for this trend to last, as it focuses on making your garden feel like less of a chore and ensuring that it is pet friendly. Perfectly manicured gardens are not the best for wildlife, and this trend can contribute to the push towards trying to help wildlife in urban areas.’\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/R8uM9rGEGEqg95LT6gvgtE-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/R8uM9rGEGEqg95LT6gvgtE-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/R8uM9rGEGEqg95LT6gvgtE-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/R8uM9rGEGEqg95LT6gvgtE-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/R8uM9rGEGEqg95LT6gvgtE-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/R8uM9rGEGEqg95LT6gvgtE-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, http